text: Barbora Růžičková (born 20 April 1998) is a Czech footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for 1. FC Slovácko and has appeared for the Czech Republic women's national team. ==Career== Růžičková has been capped for the Czech Republic national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Czech women's footballers Category:Czech Republic women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:1.
